One trusts the other and his music. It couldn't be better for us.
Your relationship with fame has not always been easy. On the other hand, thanks to your success, you could always do what you wanted.
How do you find a balance?
The way we grew has made it easier for us to find a balance.
We make sure not to be on tour too often, because it is too easy to lose this game with huge crowds who love your music.
As long as you remember that people have come because of the music, this reminds you that you have to pay attention to the music and what she has created, without being excited about being a famous rock star. That has never interest us.
