The Secretary of the Comunicaciones y Transportes - SCT (Secretariat für Kommunikation und Transport in Mexico) informed us that the results of the investigation on the accident involving the government secretary Francisco Blake Mora and other seven persons indicate that the helicopter with its entire unsharpened structure has been shot directly against the ground without the pilot being able to launch an emergency landing.
